---
const reasons = [
  'They use Pix and local payment methods — not Visa or Mastercard',
  'They expect instant payments — not 3-day processing windows',
  'They actively avoid card networks when a better option exists',
  'They will abandon a purchase if their preferred method isn\'t available',
];
---

<section class="relative py-16 sm:py-24 md:py-32">
  <div class="orb-blue absolute top-1/2 right-0 translate-x-1/2 -translate-y-1/2 opacity-50"></div>

  <div class="relative max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6">
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-16 items-center">
      <!-- Left: content -->
      <div>
        <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-3 py-1 rounded-full bg-brand-primary/10 border border-brand-primary/20 text-xs text-brand-primary mb-6">
          Why It Matters
        </div>
        <h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl md:text-4xl font-heading font-bold leading-tight mb-6">
          Your Customers Have Changed.<br />
          <span class="text-gradient-brand">Has Your Checkout?</span>
        </h2>
        <p class="text-lg text-text-secondary leading-relaxed mb-8">
          Latin American consumers are already buying globally — from luxury retail in Paris to online subscriptions in London. But they don't pay like European or American shoppers.
        </p>

        <ul class="space-y-4">
          {reasons.map((reason) => (
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="text-brand-primary mt-0.5 shrink-0" aria-hidden="true"><path d="m5 12 5 5L20 7"/></svg>
              <span class="text-text-secondary">{reason}</span>
            </li>
          ))}
        </ul>
      </div>

      <!-- Right: callout card -->
      <div class="glass-card-brand p-8 md:p-10 rounded-2xl">
        <div class="mb-6">
          <svg width="40" height="40" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="text-status-warning" aria-hidden="true"><path d="m21.73 18-8-14a2 2 0 0 0-3.48 0l-8 14A2 2 0 0 0 4 21h16a2 2 0 0 0 1.73-3Z"/><path d="M12 9v4"/><path d="M12 17h.01"/></svg>
        </div>
        <p class="text-xl md:text-2xl font-heading font-bold text-text-primary leading-snug mb-4">
          If your checkout doesn't support how they pay, <span class="text-status-warning">you don't just lose the sale — you lose the customer.</span>
        </p>
        <p class="text-text-secondary leading-relaxed">
          <strong class="text-text-primary">epagpos</strong> connects you to this demand instantly — no infrastructure overhaul, no regulatory headaches, no operational burden.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
